ADMISSION REQUIREMENTS (GENERAL)
----------------------------------
- Minimum 12 years of education (Intermediate/A-Levels/DAE or equivalent)
- Interview is required for all programs
- Merit-based selection
- For BS programs: Minimum 50% marks required (Computer Science, AI, IT, SE)
- For Arts/Commerce programs: Minimum 45% marks required
- Students with FSC Pre-Medical for CS/AI programs must pass deficiency course in Mathematics (6 credit hours)

