HOW TO APPLY
--------------
1. Visit www.mul.edu.pk
2. Click on "Admissions" section
3. Fill online application form
4. Submit required documents:
   - Matriculation (10th) certificate
   - Intermediate (12th) certificate
   - 4 passport-sized photographs
   - CNIC copy (student and parent)
   - Domicile certificate
5. Pay admission fee
6. Appear for interview (if applicable)

